7.plot: Paul London battles newcomer Desmond X for the Final Aztec Medallion; Johnny Mundo takes on the Giant Snake Man, Vibora. Jack Evans scouts XO Lishus; Cage does battle with Pentagon Dark.

9.title: A Match Made in Heaven
9.plot: Mariposa makes a proposal to Antonio Cueto. Paul London makes an offering to the Gods on behalf of the White Rabbit. The Worldwide Underground take on The Reptile Tribe in an Atomicos Match, if the Reptiles win, Johnny must join them.

10.title: A Snake Scorned
10.plot: Paul London attempts to satisfy the White Rabbit. Tensions between the Trios Champions are at an all-time high as they are forced to defend their titles against a dangerous opponent. Cage and Pentagon Dark's conflict explodes.

13.plot: Melissa Santos and Catrina engage in an epic confrontation. The Monster Matanza Cueto makes another Sacrifice to the Gods. A Luchador seeking revenge comes after Pentagon Dark. Son of Havoc observes Killshot's match.

15.title: The Hunted
15.plot: The Lucha Underground Championship and Gift of the Gods Championship are both defended. Melissa Santos and Aerostar notice a change in Fenix. Paul London pays another visit to the White Rabbit.

16.title: Kill Mil
16.plot: Ivelisse and XO Lishus find a new partner to help them face the Reptile Tribe. Jake Strong takes on Drago and Aerostar in a Nunchuck Match. A new number one contender for the Lucha Underground Championship is determined.

17.title: The Moth and the Butterfly
17.plot: The Rabbit Tribe takes on XO Lishus, Ivelisse and Joey Ryan. Marty "The Moth" Martinez introduces a new associate and sends a message to his Ultima Lucha opponent. Killshot and Son of Havoc finally go one on one.

19.title: Savagery
19.plot: Jake Strong talks with Cueto and makes demands. A Gift of the Gods Battle Royale takes place. The Mack battles his friend and former Trios Partner Killshot. A huge main event is made.

20.title: Seven to Survive
20.plot: Seven Luchadors do battle in a Seven to Survive Elimination Match for the Gift of the Gods Championship. Johnny Mundo gets some help, preparing for his match against the Monster Matanza Cueto.

21.title: Ultima Lucha Cuatro Pt. 1
21.plot: Aerostar pays a visit to an old friend. 3-Way Trios Championship Elimination Match. Taya Mundo takes on Ricky Mundo. Son of Havoc battles Killshot in match where the loser must unmask.

22.title: Ultima Lucha Cuatro Pt. 2
22.plot: El Dragon Azteca Jr. vs. Fenix, The Mack vs. Mil Muertes in a Death Match, Johnny Mundo vs. Matanza, Penatgon Dark vs. Marty "The Moth" in a Cero Miedo Match. The Order sets their plan in motion to destroy the Seven Aztec.

1.title: Welcome to the Temple
1.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple in Boyle Heights, Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Johnny Mundo vs. Prince Puma; Sexy Star vs. Son of Havoc; Blue Demon Jr. vs. Chavo Guerrero Jr.; and more content.

2.title: Los Demonios
2.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple in Boyle Heights, Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Johnny Mundo and Prince Puma vs. Cortez Castro and Mr. Cisco; Blue Demon Jr. vs. Mil Muertes; and more.

3.title: Crossing the Border
3.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple in Boyle Heights, Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's El Mariachi Loco vs. Mascarita Sagrada; Mil Muertes vs. Ricky Mandel; Drago Flores vs. Pentagon Junior vs. Rey Fenix; and much more.

4.title: Thrill of the Hunt
4.plot: "Thrill of the Hunt." Sexy Star returns to take on Ivelisse. Cueto confronts Drago, sets match against King Cuerno. Konnan warns Puma to not get involved in main event Mundo vs Big Ryck. Sexy Star vows revenge on Chavo.

5.title: Boyle Heights Street Fight
5.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple in Boyle Heights, Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Drago Flores vs. Mil Muertes; Prince Puma vs. Rycklon "Big Ryck" Stephens in a Boyle Heights Street Fight; and much more.

6.title: The Key
6.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple in Boyle Heights, Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Pimpinela Escarlata vs. Matt "Son of Havoc" Cross; Brian "Famous B" Winbush vs. Mil Muertes; Drago Flores vs. King Cuerno; and much more.

7.title: The Top of the Ladder
7.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple in Boyle Heights, Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Johnny Mundo vs. Prince Puma vs. Rycklon "Big Ryck" Stephens in a Ladder Match; Erick "Super Fly" Munoz vs. King Cuerno; and much more.

8.title: A Unique Opportunity
8.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple in Boyle Heights, Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's a Boyle Heights Battle Royal featuring: Drago Flores, King Cuerno, Pentagon Junior, Prince Puma, Rycklon "Big Ryck" Stephens; and much more.

9.title: Aztec Warfare
9.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Aztec Warfare to crown the first ever Lucha Underground Champion. Featuring: Johnny Mundo, Mil Muertes, Rey Fenix, and 17 others.

10.title: Law of the Jungle
10.plot: "Law of the Jungle." Tonight, the Lucha Underground Champion will put his title on the line. Newcomers 4-Way Elimination Match: Aerostar vs Argenis vs Angelico vs Cage. Chavo confronts Blue Demon Jr. Drago takes on King Cuerno.

11.title: Last Luchador Standing
11.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple in Boyle Heights, Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Drago Flores vs. King Cuerno in a Last Luchador Standing Match; Erick "Super Fly" Munoz vs. Pentagon Junior; and much more.

12.title: They Call Him Cage
12.plot: "They Call Him Cage." Tonight the Lucha Underground Champion puts his title on the line for the second time in just 3 weeks. 6 Man Tag Team Match: Argenis, Super Fly, AeroStar vs. Cortez Castro, Mr. Cisco and Bael.

13.title: Johnny Mundo vs. The Machine
13.plot: "Johnny Mundo vs The Machine." Cage looks to be the number one contender, but one of Lucha Undergrounds best fighters stands in his way. Surprise guest shows up to Dario Cueto's temple.

14.title: A Shot of El Patron
14.plot: "A Shot of El Patron." A new luchador arrives at the temple. Dario Cueto gives him a mic to address his fans and pledges to be the best Luchador in the World!

15.title: Eye for an Eye
15.plot: "Eye for an Eye!" Dario Cueto rewards the Crew with a No Disqualification Trios Match. Chavo finally faces Mil Muertes. Ivelisse takes matters into her own hands.

16.title: Caged Animals
16.plot: "Caged Animals." Cage looks to earn a Championship Match. Cueto offers another unique opportunity. Johnny Mundo seeks revenge.

17.title: A War Started in Mexico...
17.plot: "A War Started In Mexico..." A rivalry is renewed from Mexico, Dario Cueto pairs two luchadores with a history of bad blood. Huge Main Event.

18.title: No Escape
18.plot: "No Escape." Our Main Event gets even bigger. For the first time ever in Lucha Underground...A Steel Cage Match.

19.title: Grave Consequences
19.plot: "Grave Consequences." MASSIVE main event to come, Grave Consequences is tonight, and the only way to win, put your opponent in a coffin!

20.title: The Art of War
20.plot: "The Art of War." Two World Titles on the line... The Lucha Underground Championship is on the line and the stakes have never been higher... Boyle Heights Street Fight Main Event Championship Title Match.

21.title: Uno! Dos! Tres!
21.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple in Boyle Heights, Los Angeles, California U.S.A. its Adam "Angelico" Bridle vs. Johnny Mundo; Aero Star vs. Drago Flores; and much more.

22.title: Mask Versus Mask
22.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Dulce "Sexy Star" Garcia Rivas vs. Erick "Super Fly" Munoz in a Mask Versus Mask Match; and much more.

23.title: Fire in the Cosmos
23.plot: "Fire in the Cosmos." Best of 5 Series Drago vs Aerostar will come to and end tonight. There's one more spot left in next weeks Trios Title Match. With six of the best luchadores in the Temple, who will earn the last spot?

24.title: Trios Champions
24.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Adam "Angelico" Bridle, Ivelisse Velez and Matt "Son of Havoc" Cross vs. The Crew; and much more.

25.title: The Way of the Drago
25.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Lucha Underground Champion Prince Puma vs. Drago Flores; Rey Fenix vs. Shane "Killshot" Strickland; and much more.

26.title: The Best in the Business
26.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Lucha Underground Champion Prince Puma and Shawn Hernandez vs. Brian Cage and King Cuerno; and much more.

27.title: Ancient Medallions
27.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Alberto El Patron vs. Shawn Hernandez; Aero Star vs. Jack Evans; and much more.

28.title: Shoots and Ladders
28.plot: The Trios Titles will be defended in a Ladder Match. The first person to climb the ladder and retrieve the championships will win the titles for their team. Meanwhile, Vampiro asks Johnny Mundo to explain his actions.

29.title: Fight to the Death
29.plot: "Fight to the Death." Huge double Main Event. Fenix vs Mil Muertes Death Match. Prince Puma defends his Lucha Underground Championship Title against the #1 Contender, Hernandez. Vampiro sits down with Sexy Star.

30.title: Submit to the Master
30.plot: "Submit to the Master." Dario Cueto sets Aztec Medallion Match, Argenis vs Jack Evans. Trios Champions defend their titles against a team of DelAvar Daivari's choice. First ever Lucha Underground submission match: Sexy Star vs Pentagon Jr.

31.title: The Desolation of Drago
31.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Brian Cage vs. Drago Flores vs. King Cuerno vs. Shawn Hernandez in a #1 Contender Match; and much more.

32.title: All Night Long
32.plot: "All Night Long." Prince Puma defends his Championship Title against Johnny Mundo. By order of Dario Cueto, whichever luchador has the most pinfall and submission victories will earn the Lucha Underground Championship Title.

33.title: Death vs. The Dragon
33.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Drago Flores vs. Mil Muertes; Dulce "Sexy Star" Garcia vs. Erick "Super Fly" Munoz; and much more.

34.title: Gold and Guerreros
34.plot: "Gold and Guerreros." Drago and Hernandez meet for the first time one on one. Texano has a score to settle. The Lucha Underground Championship is on the line...Prince Puma faces Chavo and his crew for the first time ever!

35.title: Fuel to the Fire
35.plot: "Fuel to the Fire." Mundo and Alberto El Patron face each other in the ring for the first time since Alberto returned after being thrown through Cueto's window. Tonight they'll each team up with 3 others in an Atómicos Tag Team Match.

36.title: The Beginning of the End
36.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Delavar Daivari vs. Príncipe "Bengala" Odin Jr. in an Aztec Medallion Match; and much more.

37.title: PenUltimaLucha
37.plot: "PenUltimaLucha." Dario Cueto reveals the meaning of the Aztec Medallions. Texano vs. Mundo. The Mack vs. Cage. Huge Main Event: Battle Royal for the final Aztec Medallion.

38.title: Ultima Lucha - Part I
38.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Lucha Underground Trios Champions Adam "Angelico" Bridle, Ivelisse Velez and Matt "Son of Havoc" Cross vs. The Disciples of Death; and more.

39.title: Ultima Lucha - Part II
39.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Lucha Underground Champion Prince Puma vs. Mil Muertes; and much more.

1.title: A Much Darker Place
1.plot: The Luchadors return to compete, but with Dario Cueto on the run, darkness has taken over The Temple. (#40)

2.title: The Dark & the Mysterious
2.plot: Prince Puma teams with an unlikely partner; Johnny Mundo returns to The Temple with his sights set on the Lucha Underground Championship; and more. (#41)

3.title: The Hunt Is on...
3.plot: Catrina Perez enlists Lucha Underground Gift of the Gods Champion King Cuerno to help her destroy Rey Fenix. A new Luchadora debuts. (#42)

4.title: Cero Miedo
4.plot: Prince Puma takes on Pentagon Junior for the first time ever. Rey Mysterio Jr. reveals the Cueto family history. (#43)

5.title: The Machine
5.plot: Johnny Mundo battles "The Machine" Brian Cage; Juan "Texano" Aguilar Leos returns for revenge against Chavo Guerrero Jr. and The Crew; and more. (#44)

6.title: Gift of the Gods Ladder Match
6.plot: King Cuerno defends his Gift of the Gods Championship against Rey Fenix in a Ladder Match; and much more. (#45)

7.title: Death Comes in Threes
7.plot: Mil Muertes defends the Lucha Underground Championship against Pentagon Junior and Prince Puma in a 3-Way Match. (#46)

8.title: Life After Death
8.plot: Rey Fenix exchanges his Gift of the Gods Championship for a Lucha Underground Championship match; the Trios titles are defended; and more. (#47)

9.title: Aztec Warfare II
9.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Aztec Warfare 2 as twenty entrants compete for the Lucha Underground Championship. (#48)

10.title: El Jefe is Back
10.plot: Dario Cueto has returned to The Temple and is persuaded to make the new Lucha Underground Champion defend his title; the Trios Champions are in action; and more. (#49)

11.title: Bird of War
11.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Lucha Underground Champion "The Monster" Matanza Cueto vs. Rey Fenix; and much more. (#50)

12.title: Three's a Crowd
12.plot: The Trios Tournament continues and Prince Puma, Rey "El Dragon Azteca Jr." Horus and Rey Mysterio Jr. must compete; Dario Cueto redistributes the Seven Ancient Aztec Medallions and lets a new luchador compete for one; and more. (#51)

13.title: Monster Meets Monster
13.plot: Mil Muertes faces "The Monster" Matanza Cueto in a title match; Rey Fenix gets some unlikely partners in the Trios Tournament; an old rivalry is renewed over an Aztec Medallion; and more. (#52)

14.title: Cage in a Cage
14.plot: Johnny Mundo takes on Brian Cage in a Steel Cage Match for an Aztec Medallion; Four teams compete in the Trios Tournament Finals; Pentagon Junior struggles with his injuries; and more. (#53)

15.title: No Mas
15.plot: Dulce "Sexy Star" Garcia Rivas battles Melissa "Mariposa" Anderson for an Aztec Medallion in Lucha Underground's first ever "No Mas" Match; Catrina Perez confronts Dario Cueto; and more. (#54)

16.title: Graver Consequences
16.plot: From Lucha Underground Arena AKA The Temple at Boyle Heights in Los Angeles, California U.S.A. it's Lucha Underground Champion "The Monster" Matanza Cueto vs. Mil Muertes in a Grave Consequences Match; and much more. (#55)

17.title: Crime & Punishment
17.plot: Seven Luchadors compete for the Gift of the Gods Championship; Brian Cage wants back what was stolen from him; Pentagon Junior continues his dark journey with The Master; and more. (#56)

18.title: Enter the Mundo
18.plot: Lucha Underground Trios Champions Prince Puma, Rey "El Dragon Azteca Jr." Horus and Rey Mysterio Jr. defend their titles; Cortez Castro and Joey Ryan's cover gets blown; the Gift of the Gods Championship is defended. (#57)

19.title: Judgment Day
19.plot: "The Monster" Matanza Cueto defends his Lucha Underground Championship against the Gift of the Gods Champion Brian Cage; the Trios Champions defend their titles; Rey "Dragon Azteca Jr." Horus searches for his mentor's killer. (#58)

20.title: The Contenders
20.plot: Aero Star and Drago Flores face Jack Evans and PJ Black in a Nunchuck Match; Mr. Cisco learns the truth about Cortez Castro; Pentagon Junior returns to The Temple. (#59)

21.title: Six to Survive
21.plot: Six luchadors compete in the first ever Six to Survive Match for a Championship Match at Ultima Lucha Dos. (#60)

22.title: Fame & Fortune
22.plot: The 7 Ancient Aztec Medallions are redistributed; Prince Puma addresses the Believers and reveals his plans for Ultima Lucha Dos; A new luchador arrives at The Temple. (#61)

23.title: The Phoenix, the Dragon and the Spaceman
23.plot: Dario Cueto announces a new "Unique Opportunity" that can be won at Ultima Lucha Dos; Prince Puma vs. Rey "El Dragon Azteca Jr." Horus; and more. (#62)

24.title: Ultima Lucha Dos - Part I
24.plot: Son of Havoc, Cage, Texano and the Mack compete for a "Unique Opportunity" where the he winner is faced with a career defining decision.

25.title: Ultima Lucha Dos - Part II
25.plot: King Cuerno faces Mil Muertes in a Death Match; a 7-Way Gift of the Gods Elimination Match; and more. (#64)

26.title: Ultima Lucha Dos - Part III
26.plot: Rey Mysterio vs. Prince Puma. Pentagon vs. the Monster Matanza Cueto. Fenix, Drago and Aerostar vs. Worldwide Underground. Ivelisse vs. Taya. El Dragon Azteca Jr. vs. Black Lotus.

1.title: Wheel of Misfortune
1.plot: After Dario Cueto's arrest, the Luchadores return to the Temple where their destiny will be determined by the spin of a wheel. Rey Mysterio competes in the main event.

2.title: The Amulet
2.plot: Killshot and Marty "the Moth" Martinez end their bitter rivalry in the first ever Weapons of Mass Destruction Match. The power of an ancient Aztec amulet is revealed.

3.title: Ultimate Opportunities
3.plot: "Ultimate Opportunities" - Dario's Dial of Doom selects another opponent for the Monster Matanza Cueto. Dario announces that two luchaodors will compete for the "Ultimate Oppotrunity" The Trios Titles are defended.

4.title: Brothers in Broken Arms
4.plot: El Dragon Azteca Jr. takes on Chavo Guerrero with Rey Mysterio as the Guest Referee. The Worldwide Underground take on the Trios Champions and Sexy Star in an Atomicos Match. Dario is on to Cortez Castro.

5.title: The Prince and the Monster
5.plot: Dario's Dial of Doom choses another opponent for the Monster Matanza Cueto. Ivelisse has a new love interest. Killshot receives some chilling news. The Rabbit Tribe is introduced.

6.title: The Open Road to Revenge
6.plot: Rey Mysterio and Chavo Guerrero clash. Sexy Star defends her Gift of the Gods Championship against Jack Evans. Son of Havoc and Mascarita Sagrada return for revenge.

7.title: Payback Time
7.plot: Prince Puma takes on Mil Muertes. Dario's Dial of Doom choses another opponent for the Monster Matanza Cueto. Johnny Mundo is desperate for a match with Sexy Star.

8.title: Gifts of the Gods
8.plot: City Councilmen Lawrence Delgado arrives at the temple with a gift for Dario. Sexy Star defends the Gift of the Gods Championship. Rey Mysterio asks Dario for a favor.

9.title: Loser Leaves Lucha
9.plot: Rey Mysterio takes on Chavo Guerrero with the loser having to leave Lucha Underground forever. Dario spins his Dial of Doom.

10.title: Ready for War
10.plot: Prince Puma take on Mil Muertes in Grave Consequences. Mascarita Sagrada fights Famous B in a Believer's Backlash Match where the fans bring the weapons.

11.title: Aztec Warfare III
11.plot: 20 Luchadores compete for the Lucha Underground Championship in Aztec Warfare.

12.title: Every Woman Is Sexy, Every Woman Is a Star
12.plot: The Lucha Underground Championship is defended. Black Lotus returns to the Temple. Catrina confronts Jeremiah Crane. The Rabbit Tribe arrives.

13.title: Breaker of Bones
13.plot: Vampiro confronts his former student. Pentagon Dark takes on the Black Lotus Triad. Dario and his brother Matanza have different agendas.

14.title: The Bulls of Boyle Heights
14.plot: The Battle of the Bulls Tournament begins. Captain Vasquez sends Cortez Castro even deeper undercover. Kobra Moon reveals the history of her tribe.

15.title: En La Sombras
15.plot: The Battle of the Bull Tournament continues. El Dragon Azteca Jr. pays a visit to Rey Mysterio. Someone is playing mind games with Sexy Star.

16.title: The Battle of the Bulls
16.plot: The winner of the Battle of the Bulls earns a title match against the winner of Sexy Star and Johnny Mundo's Steel Cage Match. The fate of Drago is revealed.

17.title: The Gauntlet
17.plot: Cage and Texano continue their Best of Five Series for Dario's "Ultimate Opportunity". Jeremiah Crane battles Mil Muertes. A luchador returns to the Temple for revenge.

18.title: Evil Rising
18.plot: The Mack takes on Johnny Mundo with the winner getting to choose the stipulation of their Championship Match. Paul London and the Rabbit Tribe take on Kobra Moon and her Reptiles.

19.title: Gods Among Men
19.plot: El Dragon Azteca Jr. meets Lawrence Delgado and is willing to put his life on the line in a match with the Monster Matanza Cueto. Johnny Mundo confronts the Mack about their Championship Match.

20.title: All Night Long... Again
20.plot: The Mack and Johnny Mundo square off for the Lucha Underground world championship. No count outs, no disqualification, just violence, ALL NIGHT LONG

21.title: Sudden Death
21.plot: The Lucha Underground Championship is defended. Dario Cueto makes a huge announcement. Prince Puma takes on Mil Muertes in a Boyle Heights Street Fight.

22.title: The Cup Begins
22.plot: The first round of the Cueto Cup begins. Johnny Mundo and Rey Mysterio begin their training. Cage pays a visit to City Councilman Lawrence Delgado.

23.title: Family First
23.plot: The first round of the Cueto Cup continues. Marty "The Moth" Martinez's obsession with Melissa Santos resumes. Rey Mysterio and Johnny Mundo prepare to do battle.

24.title: Macho Madness
24.plot: The first round of the Cueto Cup continues. Jeremiah Crane's jealousy boils over. A new Luchador arrives at the Temple to compete in the tournament.

25.title: Left for Dead
25.plot: Dante Fox relives his time as a POW. The final matches of the first round of the Cueto Cup are fought. Rey Mysterio and Johnny Mundo continue their match preparations.

26.title: A Fenix to the Flame
26.plot: The Cueto Cup's second round begins; Marty the Moth battles Fenix; Brenda pays a visit to Texano.

27.title: Fade to Black
27.plot: The second round of the Cueto Cup continues. Vampiro advises Prince Puma on his future and his match with PJ Black. Johnny Mundo introduces his new agent to the Worldwide Underground.

28.title: Booyaka! Booyaka!
28.plot: Rey Mysterio prepares for his Lucha Underground Championship Match with Johnny Mundo by fighting PJ Black. The second round of the Cueto Cup continues. Son of Madness confronts Son of Havoc.

29.title: The Hunger Inside
29.plot: The Quarterfinals of the Cueto Cup begin. Dario has a warning for his brother Matanza. Cortez Castro checks in with Captain Vasquez. Marty The Moth's obsession with Melissa Santos grows.

30.title: Bloodlines
30.plot: The Quarterfinals of the Cueto Cup continue. An FBI agent arrives at the temple to speak with Dario Cueto. Captain Vasquez gets an unexpected visitor.

31.title: The Cup Runneth Over
31.plot: Rey Mysterio and Johnny Mundo have a confrontation. The four semifinalists in the Cueto Cup compete. Catrina sets her sights on Cage's Gauntlet.

32.title: The Cueto Cup
32.plot: Johnny Mundo threatens Dario Cueto. Two Luchadors battle for the Cueto Cup. Rey Mysterio takes on Johnny Mundo for the Lucha Underground Championship.

33.title: Havoc Running Wild
33.plot: Dario admits to his brother that he was wrong about Rey Mysterio. Son of Madness and Son of Havoc's feud runs wild. Joey Ryan pushes Cortez Castro too far.

34.title: Career Opportunities
34.plot: Dario Cueto makes a huge announcement that concerns Rey Mysterio. Cortez Castro battles Joey Ryan in a Five-O Street Fight. Johnny Mundo makes an Ultima Lucha challenge to Prince Puma.

35.title: Cien
35.plot: The 100th Episode of Lucha Underground features a star-studded Atomicos Match, El Dragon Azteca Jr. vs. Pentagon Dark, and Rey Mysterio vs. Matanza for the first time ever in the Main Event.

36.title: Rise of the Ring Announcer
36.plot: Marty "The Moth" Martinez teams with Mariposa to take on Fenix and his partner Lucha Underground's ring announcer, Melissa Santos. Plus a 7-Way Gift of the Gods Title Match. More Ultima Lucha plans are made.

37.title: Ultima Lucha Tres - Part I
37.plot: Killshot and Dante Fox's rivalry comes to an end as they fight in 2 out of 3 Falls Match called The Hell of War. Famous B competes to win Texano's contract.

38.title: Ultima Lucha Tres - Part II
38.plot: Catrina makes her in ring debut against the returning Ivelisse. Fenix faces Marty "The Moth" Martinez in a brutal "Mask vs Hair" match.

39.title: Ultima Lucha Tres - Part III
39.plot: The Gift of the Gods Championship is held high above the ring as Son of Havoc and Pentagon Dark fight for it in a ladder match. Taya Battles Sexy Star in a "last luchadora standing" match and The Mack teams up with Dante Fox and Killshot to fight for the Trios Championship.

40.title: Ultima Lucha Tres - Part IV
40.plot: Prince Puma puts everything on the line against the Lucha Underground Champion Johnny Mundo. Mil Muertes, Cage and Jeremiah Crane battle for the Gauntled of the Gods and El Dragon Asteca Jr. fights The Monster Matanza Cueto inside a Steel Cage in a night filled with violence, emotion and surprises.

locations: Boyle Heights, Los Angeles, California, USA
imdb.title: Lucha Underground
plot: Luchadores and Wrestlers from across the world, compete in the ring to be the best fighter.
